for screen brightness keys to work under i3 (on xps13), need to add file:
    /etc/X11/xorg.conf

    with this block:
    
    Section      "Device"
    Identifier   "Card0"
    Driver       "intel"
    Option      "Backlight"      "/sys/devices/pci0000:00/0000:00:02.0/drm/card0/card0-eDP-1/intel_backlight"
    EndSection
